Introduction

Cho Chanhyuk is a South Korean rapper and record producer. He first appeared in the survival show "WORLD KLASS" where he finished second place, allowing him to debut as the main dancer, lead rapper, and producer of the boy group TO1.

Chan debuted as a member of TO1 on April 1, 2020, with their first mini album Reason for Being : Benevolence.

On September 18, 2021, he released his first mixtape [Moth] under the name IRI.
